ai-tika-abh08t11:2_0: Here, how many kinds of calculation: “What is it? What is the meaning? What is that? How is it that?” “What is that?”
ai-tika-abh08t11:3_0: The meaning is: born in him possessed of the eye’s states. This is the meaning.
ai-tika-abh08t11:4_0: Another named, “Here’s calling him to take many different things!”
ai-tika-abh08t11:4_1: Should simply exist in the same way.
ai-tika-abh08t11:5_0: Previously, what is his intention, what is the way I was suspected that?
ai-tika-abh08t11:5_2: Therefore, because of that decision of wisdom, he gives his birth.
ai-tika-abh08t11:6_0: It is a woman and a man and their men, whatever other women have.
ai-tika-abh08t11:8_0: Such is the defeat of this Dhamma.
ai-tika-abh08t11:9_0: The Description of the Reference to the Origination of the World is finished.
